T1  - R&D AND ECONOMIC GROWTH IN A CASH-IN-ADVANCE ECONOMY
AU  - Chu, Angus C.
AU  - Cozzi, Guido
Y1  - 2014/05/01
PY  - 2014
DA  - 2014/05/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.12059
T2  - International Economic Review
