T1  - WAGE FLOORS, IMPERFECT PERFORMANCE MEASURES, AND OPTIMAL JOB DESIGN
AU  - Kragl, Jenny
AU  - Schöttner, Anja
Y1  - 2014/05/01
PY  - 2014
DA  - 2014/05/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.12060
